There's literally a book on him. The
Russian-born Stanford University

00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:29.729
instructor has spent a lot of time on
his toes, using relevé, rond de jambe,

00:01:29.729 --> 00:01:34.650
and plié to have his body articulate what
